13 hospital's emergency department to evaluate the patient's suspected drug
14 overdose;
15 (d) Data for each controlled substance that is reported shall include but not be
16 limited to the following:
17 1. Patient identifier;
18 2. National drug code of the drug dispensed;
19 3. Date of dispensing;
20 4. Quantity dispensed;
21 5. Prescriber; and
22 6. Dispenser;
23 (e) The data shall be provided in the electronic format specified by the cabinet
24 unless a waiver has been granted by the cabinet to an individual dispenser.
