20 designee, prior to the expiration of the one (1) year period or upon satisfactory
21 completion of one (1) year of treatment, the person shall be deemed finally
22 discharged from sentence. The secretary, or his or her designee, shall notify
23 the sentencing court of the date of[ such] discharge from the treatment or
24 recovery program.
25 (2) The secretary of the Cabinet for Health and Family Services, or his or her designee,
26 shall inform each court of the identity and location of the treatment or recovery
27 program to which the person is sentenced.
